(\\vec{r}_{1})\\right)\\cdot\\left(\\bar{\\psi}_{j}(\\vec{r}_{2})\\nabla_{r_{\
2}}\\psi_{l}(\\vec{r}_{2})\\right)=\\vec{D}_{ik}\\cdot\\vec{D}_{jl}", "state" -> 
